{"tid":2363819,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣人口首次出現下降","createTime":"2021-01-12T13:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T23:56:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3b6697aef86e3ca987faee9e5c01fa340de7c3ad","tid":2363819,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:19:58.000Z","msg":"內政部公布2020年出生人口與死亡人口，台灣首次出現負成長，也就是出生人口低於死亡人口，全國人口首次變少了。不過，從縣市來看，有些縣市人口早在10年以前就出現負成長。<br />\n<br />\n下圖是2000年到2020年，台灣每年出生與死亡人口，可以看出從2000年到2010年，出生人口就呈現逐漸減少的趨勢，在2011年跟2012年有一波反彈，但之後還是呈現逐年下降趨勢，直到2020年終於首次低於死亡人口。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZihwA2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZihwA2.jpg&h=6455c367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n針對人口負成長的情形，許多縣市在多年前就已經開始用獎金方式獎勵生育，甚至有育兒補助，但是各縣市出生人數依然持續下滑。<br />\n所以要增進人們生孩子的意願，僅憑目前的獎金獎勵方式恐怕依然不夠，而是需要改變更深層的問題，例如經濟制度與育兒環境，這些或許才是讓人們不想生孩子的根本問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/145887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F145887&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJucljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=9d7585e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/145887</a>"},{"pid":"d3ef680af778027c25d75a1a34c5536ed23abe7b","tid":2363819,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBCNTPX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBCNTPX.jpg&h=014384fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/111681\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F111681&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJucljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=1c994a0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/111681</a>"},{"pid":"3df73d8299398452f3577770fb953895aa5a64d3","tid":2363819,"uid":69157,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:32:58.000Z","msg":"台灣唔搞搞啲炒樓撚真係唔掂"},